Sama-sama.

340
00:37:20,822 --> 00:37:22,890
Manusia biasa tumbuh begitu lemah.

341
00:37:23,158 --> 00:37:24,605
Aku butuh makanan.

342
00:37:43,678 --> 00:37:45,271
Kita seharusnya tak membiarkan dia pergi.

343
00:37:45,513 --> 00:37:47,015
